1. Installation
===============
  1. Requirements:
  
          - GNU make 
          - postgresql 7.X+
          - QT2 libs (tar -C /usr/local -zxpf qt-2.3.1-gcc3.2.tgz)
  
  2. Get the source either from

       a) CVS

          mkdir xpracman-VERSION
          cd xpracman-VERSION
          cvs -d :ext:anoncvs@woody.mcmaster.wattle.id.au:/cvs co xpracman
          cd src

    or b) the source archive.

          tar -zxpf xpracman-VERSION.tgz

  3. Build and install the application

          cd xpracman-VERSION
          make all
  
  4. create database
  
          make database     (will make default db named "prac")
          or
          make database DBNAME=myname


